  <p class="note"><span data-conref="Tag_important.hts"> </span> Due to <a href="https://floating-point-gui.de/formats/fp/" target="·_blank&quot;">floating point precision issues</a>, checking to see if two values are exactly equal may return <span class="inline2">false</span>, since one may be exactly 1, while the other may be 1.00000000000001. This can be avoided by using the <a data-xref="{title}" href="../../Drag_And_Drop/Drag_And_Drop_Reference/Data_Types/Decimal_To_Integer.htm">Decimal To Integer</a> action before checking or using the &quot;greater than&quot; or &quot;less than&quot; expressions.</p>
